metadata.name: World's First Swarovski Crystals Bitcoin NFT
metadata.description:
The Genesis Artwork - a  1 meter by 0.80 meter size  (40 inch by 32 inch) physical canvas, designed by genuine pieces of Swarovski Crystals. 

This unique artwork took a full month of production work.

World's First Swarovski Bitcoin Canvas NFT

A unique 1 of 1 "Physical & Digital NFT".

We will verify the winning NFT bidder through a conversation at our twitter account  @TheNFTco_

Please provide proof of address to receive the physical artwork by FEDEX, DHL or similar shipment provider worldwide.
